title: Homestay Rio Copa
photographer_comment: FINISHED. Everything went fine. I was enchanted by a small wild bird living spontaneously in their living room. He simply made a nest in a big plant in a vase and has lived there for more than 5 years. Comming and going when he pleases. Some eggs were layed and some birds have been born since he's been there. And the owners take care of him. Soooo cute!
